-- Steinbrenner Family to Hold Private Funeral for New York Yankees' Owner
-- Jay Beberman
-- 2010-07-14T20:22:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/steinbrenner-family-to-hold-private-funeral-for-new-york-yankees-owner.html

          
          
             The family of deceased New York
Yankees principal owner George Steinbrenner said it would hold a
private funeral.  
 Details of a public memorial service will be announced next
week, the family said in a statement.  
          
          


  


        